Interface DecafTypeComponent

All Known Implementing Classes:
DTypeBox
public interface DecafTypeComponent
extends MaskComponent, com.bitwise.decaf.editor.GenericComponent

A further specification of MaskComponent for declaration fields that must provide the user with a Type-compatible input mechanism. For example, the method mask looks for (but does not require) a DecafTypeComponent as its return type field.
